The paper uses Natural Language Processing and Machine Learning techniques to classify the programming language of questions and code snippets in Stack Overflow. This suggests that the paper could belong to several sub-categories such as Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Information Retrieval (cs.IR), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Software Engineering (cs.SE), and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI). However, since the paper focuses on text classification and language identification, cs.CL and cs.IR are the most likely sub-categories.
